      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3755 - It is narrated: \"Whoever remembers Allah (swt), the Mighty and Exalted, in the marketplaces, Allah (swt) will forgive him in proportion to the number of those in it, both those who speak and those who do not.\""
